author: Nostalgia Nerd
description:
Full video at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9GyDQduKBUA ~ Everyone remembers the Game Boy; but fewer people remember the Game Master — one of the strangest handhelds from the 90s clone wars. It looked like a Game Boy, tried to act like a Game Boy, but… wasn’t quite one.

Here’s a quick look at the bizarre world of Game Boy knock-offs; cheap cartridges, odd designs, and that unmistakable 90s charm.

#GameBoy #RetroGaming #GameMaster #RetroTech #90sGaming
title: Terrible Gameboy
